research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Hughes Springs, TX, include the Mayor and five Aldermen. Information was primarily sourced from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory and the Hughes Springs city website. One Alderman's name appeared as 'Delia K. Denevan' in one source and 'Katie Denevan' in another; 'Delia K. Denevan' was used for completeness. Ryan R. Watkins is also listed as Mayor Pro Tem, but 'Alderman' is the primary elected role.
